data.description: Tastefully decorated 3 Bedroom Townhome is located in the family friendly neighborhood of Thousand Oaks. Spacious home with Chef's Kitchen, Pantry & Bar, SS Appl.; two slider access to L-Shaped Patio. You will love the Resort style amenities that are just steps away; the Clubhouse, Heated Pool, Tennis Courts, Basketball Courts, Fitness Center, Tot Play Area & Fountain Pool, plus Picnic & BBQ Areas. 24/7 Guard at Gate. Pets Allowed; no pets in unit. Easy ride to the Ocean, Palm Beach Gardens Mall and several dining and family attractions. Convenient access to I-95 and FL Turnpike.
